Class ProgramTestExecutor

java.lang.Object
assignmentevaluator.evaluationHelpers.executors.TestExecutor
assignmentevaluator.evaluationHelpers.executors.programlevel.ProgramTestExecutor
public abstract class ProgramTestExecutor extends assignmentevaluator.evaluationHelpers.executors.TestExecutor
Abstract class that represents a test executor for program-level testing. This class extends the TestExecutor class and provides common functionality for executing tests on programs (assignments).
